org.apache.flink.compiler.plan

Class OptimizedPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.compiler.plan.OptimizedPlan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitable<PlanNode>

    public class OptimizedPlan
extends Object
implements Visitable<PlanNode>
    The optimizer representation of a plan. The optimizer creates this from the user defined PACT job plan. It works on this representation during its optimization. Finally, this plan is translated to a schedule for the nephele runtime system.

             Collection<SinkPlanNode> sinks,
             Collection<PlanNode> allNodes,
             String jobName,
             Plan pactPlan)
        Creates a new instance of this optimizer plan container. The plan is given and fully described by the data sources, sinks and the collection of all nodes.
        Parameters:
        sources - The nodes describing the data sources.
        sinks - The nodes describing the data sinks.
        allNodes - A collection containing all nodes in the plan.
        jobName - The name of the PACT job
